{"id": 463, "genre": 1001, "title": "关于修图APP，你有啥想说的？", "description": "不是别人过得比你好，只是APP用得好。", "record_count": 2048, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20160606004905htaKCPEyiRNlA7wF.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2015-08-06T10:24:19Z", "options": [{"id": 7680, "content": "简直了！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157921}, {"id": 11525, "content": "一种我从来都不屑去用的东西。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 178901}, {"id": 7433, "content": "我要修人app", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142935}, {"id": 8459, "content": "照骗产量剧增", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 164080}, {"id": 7437, "content": "详情以实物为准", "image": "img/option/option/20160604234942TkDO65Xxs4FHAtIE.jpg", "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156244}, {"id": 18701, "content": "立志开发反修图，还原已修照片的app。取名（照妖镜）", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 259101}, {"id": 7438, "content": "详情以实物为准", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156244}, {"id": 7441, "content": "发朋友圈里的自拍照用来做寻人启事，一辈子也别想找到这个人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156251}, {"id": 7451, "content": "只是让自己美的更美而已…过分了就不行了…", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 156321}, {"id": 7713, "content": "修图过分的就不要晒照了，会引起众怒", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158447}, {"id": 10274, "content": "为什么女生就能修得那么漂亮男生不可以！", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 149815}, {"id": 7460, "content": "现在网友见面后报警的越来越多了#(冷)", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 151855}, {"id": 7461, "content": "一张看似随意的图起码经过了5个App的爱。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 62073}, {"id": 8485, "cont