id": 7500, "content": "哈哈", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 78325}, {"id": 7760, "content": "没钱整容患者的福音", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155086}, {"id": 7249, "content": "感觉这张脸就是为了P图而生的，可以锻炼P图技能", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 154158}, {"id": 7250, "content": "别只修自己啊，算什么好闺蜜！", "image": null, "praise_count": 123, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155075}, {"id": 7251, "content": "爱美之心人皆有之。但不能用修图欺骗别人，其他的怎么美怎么修", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 155003}, {"id": 7508, "content": "最好修的不要让我认出来", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 146245}, {"id": 7253, "content": "请经过n个app修过的图也要记得保存最高品质，不然看到糊糊的照片也很难不怀疑你修的过分啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 112307}, {"id": 7254, "content": "加滤镜加点图画文字不错，但是美颜吶，有点无脑，脸上惨白惨白的光溜溜，就很没质感，我宁愿看雀斑。", "image": null, "praise_count": 17, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 39258}, {"id": 7255, "content": "作为臭美及互联网人士 手机里竟无一款修人像图工具 说明这种事儿因人而异 有大量的人用美肤液化 也一定有大量的人不用啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 129275}, {"id": 7256, "content": "人类很纠结，费尽心机得到的细节总是轻易丢掉。", "image": "img/option/option/20160605211134n1PBTqy3NDVkRztc.jpg", "praise_count": 30, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2557}, {"id": 7257, "content": "自己骗自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 55, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 142461}, {"id": 7513, "content": "层次丰富", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157039}, {"id": 7514, "content": "有本事一辈子不出现在人前 每次见面都觉得跟照片长得不一样 照骗骗谁啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157058}, {"id": 7262, "content": "看图得脑补和卸妆", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 127867}, {"id": 7264, "content": "大家各有各的不足，起码要用到3款app才能基本满意", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1493}, {"id": 7776, "content": "向上的价值观啊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 158709}, {"id": 7268, "content": "被人骗买了一个30块的修图APP，觉得不如免费的好", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 114367}, {"id": 7269, "content": "美不美，一盆水。没滤镜，全是鬼。", "image": null, "praise_count": 157, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138266}, {"id": 7526, "content": "如果每个人死了都变成一本书，  有的人变成了传奇，  有的人变成了禁书， 我想说的是有的人变成了美图秀秀使用手册。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 147410}, {"id": 7271, "content": "除了VSCOcam，其他都退散吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 58260}, {"id": 7535, "content": "现在都是手机制造美女", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 157098}]}